自定义字体和代码 字体选择的是LXGW WenKai/霞鹜文楷，参考其网页嵌入实现1,2，在layouts/partials/extend_head.html中插入HTML代码
&lt;link rel=&#34;stylesheet&#34; href=&#34;https://cdn.staticfile.org/lxgw-wenkai-screen-webfont/1.6.0/style.css&#34; /&gt; 在assets/css/extended/blank.css中插入CCS即可，Consolas是本博客采用的字体
/*字体*/ body { font-family: &#34;LXGW WenKai Screen&#34;, sans-serif !important; } code { font-family: &#34;LXGW WenKai Screen&#34;, sans-serif; } /*code*/ .post-content pre, code { font-family: &#39;Consolas&#39;, sans-serif; max-height: 40rem; }

